<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1907/505710.jpg" alt="Aakash Bramdeo" width="454" height="362">Aakash Bramdeo<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1907/505711.jpg" alt="Sandile Mdadane" width="232" height="362">Sandile MdadaneWe would like to thank him for his instrumental role at the Sunday Tribune and wish him well in his new role. We also thank Regional Executive Editor and Editor of The Mercury, Yogas Nair, for so wonderfully holding the reins of Post these past months and driving up its circulation. Sandile Mdadane, the current Weekend Editor at Isolezwe, has been appointed Acting Editor of the Sunday Tribune. We are excited about the renewed focus on digital first and enterprise journalism that Sandile will bring to our premier Sunday newspaper in KZN. We wish him great success.